Vicon Marker




1. HEAD (5 = 1 + 2 * 2)

Ariel - center
LFHD - left front head
LBHD - left back head
RFHD - right front head
RBHD - right back head

2. THORAX SAGITTAL PLANE (4 = 2 * 2)

C7 - back neck
T10 - back center

Clav - clavicle (front neck)
Strn - Sternum (front center)


3. SHOULDER, ARM, and HAND (20 = 10 * 2)

LFSH - left front shoulder
LBSH - left back shoulder
LUPA - left upper arm
LELB - left elbow
LIEL - left inner elbow
LFRM - left front arm
LIWR - left inner wrist
LOWR - left outter wrist
LIHAND - left inner hand
LOHAND - left outter hand
RFSH - right front shoulder
RBSH - right back shoulder
RUPA - right upper arm
RELB - right elbow
RIEL - right inner elbow
RFRM - right front arm
RIWR - right inner wrist
ROWR - right outter wrist
RIHAND - right inner hand
ROHAND - right outter hand


4. WAIST (6 = 3 * 2)

LFWT - left front waist
MFWT - middle front waist
RFWT - right front waist
LBWT - left back waist
MBWT - middle back waist
RBWT - right back waist


5. LEGS (8 = 4 * 2)

LTHI - left thigh
LKNE - left knee
LKNI - left knee inner
LSHN - left shin
RTHI - right thigh
RKNE - right knee
RKNI - right knee inner
RSHN - right shin


6. FEET (10 = 5 * 2)

LANK - left ankle
LHEL - left heel
LMT5 - left outter toe
LMT1 - left inner toe
LTOE - left toe
RANK - right ankle
RHEL - right heel
RMT5 - right outter toe
RMT1 - right inner toe
RTOE - right toe
